{"tid":1546194,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚無啦啦被人踢岀TKO公海 好撚嬲(發洩post)","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T08:23:21.000Z","uid":206951,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05b55b00a378a39ee1a715c8a7cbb66a4d201f6e","tid":1546194,"uid":206951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">是咁的小弟啱啱就係TG屌尻啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">散水撚</span></span><br />\n點知入面個個都屌返我 一個人都冇幫過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我炆得制爆咗句將軍澳輸人哋幾條街<br />\n我就咁俾人踢走咗 可能真係我錯！<br />\n但我地手足唔係講過要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span>嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你要迫人聽你講要散要人返屋企呢？<br />\n唔散就屌 係到搞分化 不停叫人走 唔走嘅就話佢哋想死嘅就自己留返係到去送頭 仲話完成咗任務 叫人走 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">狗走咗未？站封咗未？</span></span> 啲狗先啱啱上車嚟增援就叫人散 <br />\nBe water好重要 但冇hit齋run有撚用呀？不如唔好岀嚟呀笨 岀到嚟咩都冇就走 真係嘥尻氣<br />\n對面睇撚到咁樣實照食住我哋上啦 你又唔係唔知啲狗最鍾意人哋散水個時嚟個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大捕獲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁淆底仲好意思學人挽抗爭？<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你知唔知道你哋咁做會害死幾多前線嘅呢？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係上次東涌個班散水黨 搞到啲人係公路棄哂gear<br />\n最後行到收費站一隻狗影都唔見 我就係啲勇武 你知唔知道你哋搞到佢地有幾驚 有幾絕望？<br />\nBe water啫 而唔係對方啱啱岀增援就話要返屋企 最興就係話聽日再挽過 講真有幾多個會日日岀嚟挽過？ 之後第二日又講返同一句嘢 你估個個真係住附近嘅咩？ 話散就散到咩？<br />\n咁死啦 郁啲就返屋企 咁我哋如果岀添馬 上環 維園 係咪都聽到人哋有增援就散水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">明唔明咩叫流水 咩叫散水呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得我叫人be water轉場挽其他地鐵站 都唔好散住<br />\n有人答我周街都係狗 仲去挽？去你屋企挽啦！<br />\n咁其實坑口仲多狗 點解仲咁多人去？<br />\n你咁驚狗 你仲岀街？都講到明撚狗 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">冇狗點撚狗呀</span></span>大佬？<br />\n你老味你一直mon撚住個mon 你有冇岀嚟幫到手？<br />\n唔該咁多位香港人 爭氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怯就輸成世<br />\n無心得罪咁多位 如果真係嘅 對唔住 sorry for 1999<br />\n記住每個革命成功都係要堅持 對住強權唔好退縮<br />\n終有一日我哋會成功<br />\n大家繼續跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊<br />\n香港人加油</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoxrnYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoxrnYe.jpg&h=29f4b250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaqHFVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaqHFVR.jpg&h=be9ce4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHfTNAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHfTNAS.jpg&h=dcc8797c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"995bf77739d554c333422608b96e36dfcb8a3d23","tid":1546194,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54b8d49972f215c0c9218e705bf481c964de043b","tid":1546194,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ab6c9e3f1aec81c4f11a42a88f4f3e9fdee34","tid":1546194,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:52:35.000Z",